             were indicted for that <rs id="t17821016-43-off223" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17821016-43-off223" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17821016-43-off223" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>
               they before the said felony, on the said 12th of September last, did unlawfully and feloniously, aid, counsel, abet, and procure the said 
                     <persName id="t17821016-43-person492">
                        Isaac
                         Votear
