                  </persName>
            , did before the said felony, unlawfully and feloniously, aid, counsel, abet, and procure the said 
               <persName id="t17821016-43-person498">
                  Isaac
                   Votear
               <interp inst="t17821016-43-person498" type="surname" value="Votear"></interp>
